<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><id>https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0</id><title>HKDiscuss house</title><updated>2025-06-03T03:35:36.279131+00:00</updated><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0"/><generator uri="https://lkiesow.github.io/python-feedgen" version="1.0.0">python-feedgen</generator><subtitle>Latest articles</subtitle><entry><id>db9647a628003b41fdaefca333198cea</id><title>樓市重擊 | 據報羅兵咸永道香港本月有50名合夥人離職</title><updated>2025-06-02T20:24:45+08:00</updated><author><name>買樓唔好搞阿叔</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-02T20:24:45+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572672041"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572672041"&gt;裁員潮減薪潮持續, 我都無眼睇啦, 見步行步啦&lt;br&gt;硬好: 樓價一定升&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;《經濟通通訊社2日專訊》據《香港01》引述消息報道，羅兵咸永道香港辦事處於本月有50名合伙人離職，因被勸退、辭退及自行離職等，同時多個部門員工被減薪，幅度最少兩成至三成。報道引述羅兵咸表示不作評論。&lt;br/&gt;…&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://invest.hket.com/article/3958392/%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E7%BE%85%E5%85%B5%E5%92%B8%E6%B0%B8%E9%81%93%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%88%E6%9C%8950%E5%90%8D%E5%90%88%E5%A4%A5%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A2%E8%81%B7" target="_blank" uhash="2681d79b281b648d684223d5173c2b87"&gt;https://invest.hket.com/article/3958392/據報羅兵咸永道香港本月有50名合夥人離職&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31945364&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1208639309683e6d8877d9d2_15199807"/><published>2025-06-02T20:24:45+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>699032bf1462bf2f90cef529618abbd3</id><title>不招人妒是庸才, 硬好都認同我睇中樓市下跌</title><updated>2025-06-02T20:38:43+08:00</updated><author><name>買樓唔好搞阿叔</name></author><content