&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572597857"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572597857"&gt;老公失業5個月，佢話已經SEND咗73份CV，但一份工都冇見過！&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;佢話見好多公司不停登廣告請人，但就唔會安排人面試！&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;有幾間公司係老公本行業，本職位，老公勝任有餘，老公重複申請二至三次都冇安排面試！&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;到底咩心態不停登廣告就係唔請人，唔面試？&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31940384&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=1057&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-05-28T13:57:48+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>aef9b3d92d58b0ff281daba254c7e883</id><title>想考CPA增值自己，會唔會都係個好選擇？</title><updated>2024-11-27T15:34:54+08:00</updated><author><name>老千蛋白質</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2024-11-27T15:34:54+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_569866833"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_569866833"&gt;本身喺Inhouse Finance 做咗5年幾嘢，平時做嘢都睇開Financial Report同Forecasting，一路都冇考牌但最近越嚟越覺得，考返個CPA牌會更加幫到自己升上去......&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;不過始終都成30幾歲人，要由頭讀起十幾科，對我嚟講就真係有啲吃力，想問吓有冇方法可以考得快啲？&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31769994&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=1057&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2024-11-27T15:34:54+08:00</published></entry></feed>